org.tinylog.writers

Class AbstractFormatPatternWriter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.tinylog.writers.AbstractFormatPatternWriter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Writer
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ConsoleWriter, FileWriter

    public abstract class AbstractFormatPatternWriter
extends Object
implements Writer
    Base writer for outputting rendered log entries. The format pattern will be read from property format.
